&lt;h2&gt;Plasma myndavélafesting fyrir Autodarts&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="plasma-myndavélafesting-fyrir-autodarts"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#plasma-myndav%c3%a9lafesting-fyrir-autodarts" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Þetta er &amp;ldquo;Plasma&amp;rdquo; festingin, vinsæll valkostur sem er hannaður til að sitja beint á píluborðinu og veitir stöðugt og gott sjónarhorn fyrir myndavélarnar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;
&lt;img src="https://autodarts.diy/3d-printing/images/plasma_assembly_git.png" title="Fullgerð myndavélafesting" alt="Mynd af prentaðri myndavélafestingu" loading="lazy" /&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;Fullgerð myndavélafesting&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Mynd fengin frá &lt;a href="https://autodarts.diy/3d-printing/"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;opinberu Autodarts DIY síðunni&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Prentunarráðleggingar&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="prentunarráðleggingar"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#prentunarr%c3%a1%c3%b0leggingar" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Efni:&lt;/strong&gt; PLA eða PETG&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lagahæð:&lt;/strong&gt; 0.2mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fylling (Infill):&lt;/strong&gt; 20%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stuðningur (Supports):&lt;/strong&gt; Gæti þurft stuðning fyrir myndavélarhaldarann (Cam Holder), fer eftir prentara.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Niðurhal&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="niðurhal"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#ni%c3%b0urhal" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Þú getur sótt allar STL skrár fyrir Plasma festinguna á GitHub síðu Autodarts:
&lt;a href="https://github.com/autodarts/docs/tree/main/static/3d-printing/stl"title="Smelltu til að opna GitHub möppuna"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sækja Plasma Mount skrár á GitHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Frekari upplýsingar&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="frekari-upplýsingar"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#frekari-uppl%c3%bdsingar" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fyrir fleiri hönnunarmöguleika og upplýsingar, skoðaðu opinberu Autodarts DIY síðuna:
&lt;a href="https://autodarts.diy/3d-printing/"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;autodarts.diy/3d-printing/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>